Product Name: Indel B TB20 BT DT 12-24v Compressor Coolbox
Product Description:
Indel B TB20 BT DT 12-24v Compressor Coolbox

High performance 20 litre cooler

Indel B's 20 litre coolbox gives you effortless cooling performance in a compact package. The TB20 DT features dual temperature zones, using an internal divider to allow you to create two areas with different temperature levels. These temperature zones can be easily controlled by the elegant black ribbon control panel on the lid of the cooler, allowing you to dial in the exact temperature you desire for your food and drinks. This means you can use one zone to chill your beers perfectly, and another to keep food frozen, for example. 

Control your cooling without leaving your chair

Fancy keeping your feet up next holiday? Indel B's iOS and Android smartphone app allows you to set the temperature of your coolbox straight from your phone. The app communicates with your coolbox via Bluetooth, providing real-time temperature control. Temperatures as low as -18°C can be selected, making this a capable freezer as well as a cooler.

Lightweight and elegant

The coolbox uses a lightweight design, with flush handles and a sleek silver finish. It also includes an internal light, perfect for evening parties.

Product Description:
Indel B LiON X30A Portable Battery Powered Coolbox

Up to 21 hours of cooling on one charge

Indel B's LiON cooler is perfect for off-grid adventures. This compact 30-litre coolbox features an integrated lithium ion battery - the same type of battery that provides your laptop or smartphone with a long battery life. The battery found in this cooler is much larger however, providing 400Wh of power to keep your cooler active for up to 21 hours of performance.

Stay cool anywhere

The battery life of this cooler makes it ideal for day trips, allowing you to charge ahead of your trip and not have to worry about your food and drinks perishing. The two rubber wheels, and retractable pull handle, ensure it can follow you wherever you go, too.

Easy control

The integrated digital display makes it easy to set your ideal temperature for the cooler, letting you perfect your cooling. Fancy staying in your chair? You can also connect to the cooler via a Bluetooth connection, allowing you to control the cooler via the Indel B smartphone app for Android and iOS.

Outwell Deep Cool 28L Compressor Fridge Freezer Cooler

Powerful compressor coolbox can cool as low as -18 °C

Perfect for camping, campervans and more, this high-power cooler ensures none of your food goes to waste. This coolbox allows you to specify your desired temperature via the LED display, letting you achieve perfectly chilled drinks or safely frozen food. The selectable temperature ranges from -18 °C to +10 °C, making it a great fridge or freezer.

Portable design

The corners of the coolbox are also reinforced, ensuring it can withstand whatever life throws at it. Fancy taking the party back indoors? The included 230v adapter ensures it can run off a household mains supply, too. This great for when you're at a campsite with mains hookup too, allowing you to preserve the batteries in your campervan, caravan or motorhome.

Quiet performance

Outwell have equipped this cooler with an efficient compressor, built with sound suppression in mind, which means the cooler shouldn't disturb your sleep. The removeable lid opens both left and right, and the internal basket can be removed if desired also.

  • LED display and control
  • 28L volume
  • Removeable lid can open both left and right
  • Robust spring-loaded handles
  • Operates on 12v or 230v (with included 230v adapter)

Product Description:
Thule Fabric Clamps for Awnings and Tensions Rafters

Eliminates flapping fabric noise

For those camping in windy environments, awning fabric may flap against itself and the tension rafter, creating an unpleasant noise, and placing strain on the awning. These fabric clips simply clip onto your tension rafter, and clamp onto your awning fabric, creating a more secure connection between the two. Thule have given these clips a 'universal' design, ensuring they will fir onto most tension rafters - but your experience may vary.

One set contains two clips. 

This awning fabric clamp is compatible with:

  • Oval side rafter on Thule G2 Rain and Sun Blockers
  • Thule Tension Rafter G2
  • Square telescopic tension rafter on Thule Omnistor 1200
  • May work with many other awnings due to universal design

Outwell Deep Chill 29 Litre Coolbox

Compact coolbox with the power to freezer to -20°C

Outwell's Deep Chill range of coolboxes offer slimline, compact refrigeration. Perfect for both the home and beyond, this cooler can be run on 12v or with the included 230v adapter - and even comes with an adapter for European plugs.

Anti vibration technology keeps noise levels down, and anti-tilt features keep the compressor running at angles of up to 40 degrees. Undervoltage protection ensures your battery will not be drained too low as to cause damage, too. The rugged steel body makes this cooler perfect for adventure.

Product Description:
Avtex 18.5" HD Smart TV with One Touch Tuning

Built-in access to on demand TV including BBC iPlayer

The AV195TS is the most compact Avtex Smart TV and provides all the benefits of a fully smart television with the dimensions to fit the smallest of spaces.

The latest Avtex AV195TS is a a 12/24V DC/240V dual tuner Smart HD television with the latest Avtex Vidaa mobile Smart platform designed for caravans and motorhomes. Packed with features and content. This smart platform not only provides access to the premium streaming services such as Netflix, Amazon Prime, Disney+, YouTube all the catchup services such as iPlayer, ITVX, All4, My5, Freeview Play and much more. The latest Avtex Smart TV features AQT easy tuning system and an onscreen leisure battery meter with integrated intelligent power supply. These features are exclusive to Avtex TVs and perfect for caravan and campervan touring.

Bluetooth Connectivity  

With built in Bluetooth connectivity the AV195TS connects to devices such as the Avtex SB195BT sound bar or bluetooth headphones. Compatible with both Android or Apple (iOS) devices, gives the ability to share photos, movies and music content. In addition to the standard remote control you can control your TV easily with your mobile phone using the Vidaa App. Watch Full HD in your caravan or campervan through your regular aerial or satellite dish without the need for extra equipment.

Made for campervans, caravans, motorhomes and boats

This television can run off a 12v/24v DC supply or a 240v AC mains supply, perfect for leisure use. An on-screen battery meter is available, and the ultra-compact edge-to-edge design is perfect for saving space.

With all the amenities you'd expect from a home kitchen - in your campervan

You don't have to settle for less when you go travelling in your campervan, caravan, motorhome or boat. Thetford's compact Argent 3 hob still manages to house three powerful and efficient gas burner, each with 12v ignition and individual controls. The sink comes complete with a drainer for all of your washing up, too.

Includes tap, water tanks, pump, regulator, piping and fittings

This kit is designed to give you everything you need to get your campervan started, whether you're a beginner or an expert. We've included a set of water tanks, as well as food-safe water piping, a reliable 12v pump and a lightweight tap. To complete your gas system, we've included a regulator and piping, allowing you to connect a gas cylinder to your stovetop.

Choose the options that suit your van

We've provided a range of options so you can customise this kit to fit your needs. Please see below for the full contents of what is supplied with each regulator option, and use the options above to select your choice. We recommend the bulkhead regulator for permanent installations.

Thetford Argent 3 Burner Hob and Sink Conversion Kit 1:

•    Thetford Argent 3 burner hob 
•    Thetford Argent sink with drainer
•    Reich Samba Micro Switch Cold Tap or Hot & Cold Tap
•    Whale Submersible Pump
•    2 x 9.5L Jerry Cans

•    2mtr x 10mm Cold Pipe
•    2mtr x 20mm Waste Pipe
•    2mtr x 10mm Hot Pipe (Only available when mixer tap selected)
•    1 x 75mm Vent

•    Pack of x 5 P Clips
•    4 x Jubilee Clips

Camping Gaz:

•    1x Camping Gaz Regulator
•    1x 8mm Compression Nozzle
•    1mtr LPG Gas Hose

Bulkhead Option includes:

•    1 x 8mm Bulkhead Regulator
•    1 x 45cm Pigtail
•    1 x 8mm 90° Compression Elbow
•    1 x Gaz Adapter
•    2mtr x 8mm Copper Pipe
•    1x 8mm Straight Compression Coupling

Robust battery isolator to protect and secure vehicle ignition systems

This heavy duty battery isolator switch lets you safely isolate and disable your battery from your alternator and other electrical systems. Your van, car or campervan's 12v feed from your battery system can be switched off by use of the red key, preventing ignition. 

Designed to keep your electrical systems safe

This isolator includes a resistor to be wired through the ground earth connection, which supresses any alternator surge spikes and ensures they won't damage your system.

Product Description:
Ridged Roof Adapter for Rooflights - Ducato/Relay/Jumper/Boxer - DU4040

Fits into the ridges in your campervan's roof to give you a level surface

This innovative new roof adapter is designed to simplify the installation of rooflights with Peugeot Boxer, Citroën Jumper and Fiat Ducato vans from 2007 onwards. The frame sits flush against the ridges and channels in your van's roof, providing a level and smooth mounting surface for a rooflight.

Designed to weather the elements

Compatible with many popular rooflights

The frame's aperture measures 40x40cm, making it the perfect size for many 40x40 rooflights such as the MaxxFan MaxxAir, Thule Omnivent, Dometic Seitz Mini Heki, Fiamma Crystal 400x400 and MPK 400x400.

DU4040 Roof Adapter Features:

  • Thule Omnivent roofvent
  • Dometic Seitz Mini Heki rooflight

Product Name: FireAngel Carbon Monoxide Alarm
Product Description:
FireAngel Carbon Monoxide Alarm

Trusted carbon monoxide alarm with 7 year warranty

Wherever gas is used, there's a chance that dangerous carbon monoxide may be released. FireAngel's carbon monoxide brings you peace of mind, giving both an audible and visual signal when dangerous levels of carbon monoxide are detected. 

Why is carbon monoxide worth monitoring?

Carbon monoxide is odourless, colourless and tasteless. This means it can build up in your campervan, caravan, motorhome or boat without you becoming aware. It can cause unconsciousness, brain damage and ultimately death. Potential sources of carbon monoxide, or CO, include ovens, cars, boilers, gas cookers, open fires, BBQ's and more.

Easy to service

With replaceable batteries, you don't have to dispose of the unit when the batteries are done. You can place the unit wherever is ideal for you too, since it doesn't require a wired connection.

Product Name: Adventurer (CRV) Campervan Top Hinge Window with Blind and Fly Screen - Flush Acrylic Glass
Product Description:
Adventurer (CRV) Camper Van Top Hinged Window Aluminium Framed with Dual Blinds

Refined new windows with aluminium metal frame

A new range of top hinged campervan windows from Jacksons. With a lightweight white gloss inner frame and a robust aluminium external frame, this top hung camper van window by Adventurer will keep your van secure. Smooth anti-UV and privacy tinted acrylic gives you a spotless view of your environment, too.

Simple and robust child lock catches

The window struts give you a smooth and reliable window operation. The latches also feature child-lock controls to prevent them from being opened unintentionally.

Elegant magnetic dual blind system

The inner frame features two integrated blinds - both a fly screen and a full blind. The fly screen is made of a fiberglass mesh, giving it a rugged durability and allowing ventilation. The full blind has a reflective rear to keep your camper-van, caravan or motor home insulated. You can also mix-and-match your use of these top hinge blinds, with magnets allowing them to hold position in the middle, and black tensioning screws allowing you to easily adjust tension at the top.

Adventurer top hung campervan window features:

  • Double glazed
  • Powder-coated aluminium metal frame
  • Anti-UV coating
  • Privacy tinted 
  • Lightweight acrylic glass
  • Robust stainless steel struts (except 2 models - see table below)
  • Child lock latches let you fix window in position
  • Fibreglass mesh fly-screen with ventilation
  • Top hinged campervan windows for easy install for wall thicknesses of 22-35mm
  • Insulated blind
  • Magnetic blind system
  • Easy blind tension adjustment via screw
  • Suitable for caravans, motorhomes, campervans and horseboxes

CBE BMTCO Carbon Monoxide Gas Detector - 232802
Product Description:
CBE BMTCO Carbon Monoxide Gas Detector - 232802

Keep your family safe around gas appliances

This 12v carbon monoxide (CO) detector provides an audible warning when CO levels reach dangerous levels in your campervan, caravan, motorhome or boat.

Why do I need a carbon monoxide alarm?

Carbon monoxide is colourless, odourless and tasteless - unlike carbon dioxide, it's completely imperceptible. It can cause you to fall unconscious without warning, and can ultimately lead to death. It's a common by-product of incomplete combustion, which can occur if gas is burned incorrectly. That's why an alarm is essential - it provides a warning that your health may be at risk.

Includes frame and backbox

This CBE detector includes a flush frame, making it perfect for installation in campervans, caravans and motorhomes. It runs off a standard 12v supply, too.

CBE BMTCO Carbon Monoxide Gas Detector features:

  • Audible alarm for dangerous CO levels
  • Sensor has approx 10 year lifespan
  • Uses 12v DC supply
  • Includes flush frame
  • Tested and calibrated for CO

Product Name: Adventurer Low Profile Campervan Window with Top Hinge, Blinds & Flyscreen - Flush Acrylic Glass and Frame
Product Description:
Adventurer Campervan Motorhome Low Profile Flush Window with Top Hinge, Blinds & Fly screen

The Adventurer Campervan Window combines a stylish low-profile design with the durability needed for life on the road. Its lightweight yet robust aluminium frame, powder-coated for weather resistance, protects against the elements. Double-glazed acrylic keeps your van comfortable year-round, offering excellent insulation and extra UV protection too from a powdered coating with a matte black paint. Perfect for motorhomes, caravans, campervans & horseboxes.

The windows use high-quality acrylic with an anti-UV and privacy coating, keeping your van cooler in summer and warmer in winter. For added convenience, the window features built-in adjustable blinds with a reflective lining for superior temperature control. A breathable mesh fly screen keeps unwanted insects at bay while allowing ventilation. Stainless steel latches ensure the window can be secured at any desired angle or fully closed for safety. Two sliding blinds fit inside the inner window frame, giving you fully adjustable control the light and heat entering your motorhome or campervan. The blind features a reflective lining to insulate your van from extreme temperatures, and the mesh fly screen keeps unwanted pests from entering your caravan campervan or motorhome while allowing ventilation. The Adventurer FSH Window also has a latch system built into the stainless steel strut's handles which lets you secure the windows at the angle you desire (up to 70°), or to fix them closed with the secure latch system to keep your family safe. 

Features:

  • Built to Last: The frame is constructed from high-quality, powder-coated aluminium alloy for excellent weather resistance and a touch of style.
  • Double Glazed Acrylic: Lightweight and shatter-resistant acrylic provides excellent insulation and UV protection, keeping your van cooler in summer and warmer in winter.
  • Complete Comfort:
    • Adjustable Blinds: Two built-in blinds with a reflective lining offer complete control over light and heat.
    • Fly Screen: A breathable mesh screen keeps unwanted insects at bay while allowing fresh air circulation.
    • Privacy Tinting: Enjoy a touch of privacy with the lightly tinted acrylic.
  • Secure and Easy to Use:
    • Top Hinge Design: This window allows for easy installation in vans with walls between 22mm and 35mm thick.
    • Secure Latch System: Stainless steel latches allow you to secure the window at any desired angle or keep it firmly closed. The window’s safety catches prevent it from being opened from the outside.
    • Child Safety Locks: Built-in child lock latches provide added peace of mind.
  • Customizable: This window comes in a sleek, square design.
  • Magnetic blind system for easy removal and cleaning
  • Adjustable blind tension
  • Easy lever latch system

Product Description:
Maxxair SkyMaxx Caravan Campervan & Motorhome Roof Light

400 x 400 Rooflight with built in blind and fly screen 

Maxxair have all installations in mind with the SkyMaxx this 400 x 400 can be used as a replacement for another model or as a new installation on a brand new vehicle. Easily adjust the blind and flyscreen to shade your living space and to keep insects out.

Innovative Design

The Maxxair Skymaxx is supplied as standard with user interchangeable panels allowing you to switch between "vented" and "non-vented".

Vented

Allows the air to flow into the van at all times even when the dome is closed, this is normally standard for caravans but not recommended for campervans and motorhomes.

Non-Vented

When the roof light dome is closed the complete rooflight is sealed meaning that no air can get in, this is recommended as having air flow in a campervan or motorhome can lead to a whistling sound while driving.

 

Features:

  • Optional LED Light with SkyMaxx Plus
  • Manual opening with 3 different positions
  • Built in pleated blind with flyscreen
  • Fits all 400 X 400 roof openings
  • Forced and Non-Forced ventilation 
  • Installs in 23-60mm roof thickness' (No Cutting or Adapters Required)

Inflatable Caravan Touring Awning

With single-point inflation

Product Name: Alde 3020 Compact HE Boiler - 7.5kW LPG 230v
Product Description:
Alde 3020 Compact HE Boiler - 7.5kW LPG 230v

Compact, reliable and highly efficient

Alde's 3020 High Efficiency boiler is perfect for use in central heating systems in large campervans, caravans, motorhomes and boats. With 7.5kW of power, it can provide plenty of hot water and heating. The boiler contains a 8 litre water tank inside, allowing hot water to be stored for use.

The ubiquitous caravan heater - tried and trusted design

Alde's 3020 boiler has been used for many years in caravans, campervans, motorhomes, boats and more. The design has been favoured by caravan manufacturers and converters alike for it's reliability, efficiency and compact dimensions. The boiler's internal heat exchanger uses an innovative design featuring three concentric cylinders. These are the combustion chamber, the central heating cylinder and the hot water cylinder. Aluminium is used where possible to save weight.

Easy installation and operation

All connections for the boiler are located along one long side, leaving the other sides free for flush installation. Two electric 230v heating elements are included, offering up to 3150w of heating. It also uses a multi-stage gas burner system, allowing gas to be used as efficiently as possible. The microcontroller based boiler control can be linked to Truma's air conditioning systems, providing a unified climate control system.

Alde 3020 Compact HE boiler features:

  • 7.5kW of heating power
  • Twin 230v heating elements with 3150w of power
  • 8 litre onboard hot water tank
  • Lightweight design
  • Operates on propane, butane or 230v
  • All connections interface on a single side

Vitrifrigo VTR5040 ES 3 Way Caravan LPG 240v 12v Fridge

We currently have 1x VTR5040 ES fridge in stock available for 2-3 working day delivery. Call us to check up-to-date availability. 

The Vitrifrigo VT5040 fridge is a compact 3-way gas and electric fridge that is suitable for the installation in small caravans where space is at a premium.

Small in size, fully featured.

Despite its compact size, the VTR5040 3 way fridge from Vitrifrigo boasts an impressive 40 litres capacity, and is still able to operate on LPG butane / propane gas, 230V AC mains electric, and 12v DC leisure battery. The VTR5040 fridge has an electric thermostat and 3-position gas valve allowing the user to manual control the desired power source. The Vitrifrigo VTR5040 caravan fridge also features a reversible door allowing it to be opened on either a left or right hinge.

The nearest replacement for the Dometic RM123 3-way fridge

The dimensions of the Vitrifrigo VTR5040 refrigerator mean it is now the nearest replacement in terms of size to the now discontinued Dometic / Electrolux RM123 fridge installed in many small caravans. It may also serve as a replacement for those looking to replace the Dometic RM122 with a 3-way gas model.

Vitrifrigo VTR5040 LPG Compact Caravan Fridge Dimensions

  • Height: 590mm

Product Name: Reich 19L Twin Submersible Water Pump with Non-Return Valve
Product Description:
Reich 19L Twin Water Pump with Non-Return Valve - RK26

Submersible pump with dual pump system

Reich's innovative design of this submersible pump offers improved reliability and smoother operation. Twin pumps provide a smoothed, even flow, reducing vibrations. And if one pump fails, the unit will still operate at a reduced flow rate.

Thetford Triangular Corner Hob and Sink Camper Van Conversion Kit
Product Description:
Thetford Triangular Corner Hob & Sink Campervan Conversion Kit

Complete with tap, pipes, water tanks, pump and gas regulator

With all the essentials to create a quality campervan conversion, we've created this kit to make it easy to get your campervan started. At the heart of this kit is a matching set of a Thetford triangular hob and sink, perfect for use in the corners of your camper. We've also included gas, water and waste pipes, a 12v pump, gas regulator, water tanks, a tap and more - saving you the hassle of finding compatible equipment!

Simple and sleek units with glass lids

Thetford's triangular hob uses space efficiently, spacing three hobs evenly across its surface. The bowl and the hob both use stainless steel, with glass lids giving you extra room in your campervan, caravan, motorhome or boat when not in use. The gas hob cooker uses 12v ignition for easy start-up, too.

Customise to create your ideal conversion

You can customise this kit with the options above to select either left or right hand stovetop cooker or basin sink. It's the perfect starter kit for campervan conversions. We also offer either a gaz or bulkhead gas regulator setup for this kit - we recommend the bulkhead for permanent set-ups. 

Thetford Triangular Hob & Sink Conversion Kit Features:

•    Thetford Triangular Hob
•    Thetford Triangular Sink
•    Reich Samba Micro Switch Cold Tap or Hot & Cold Tap
•    Whale Submersible Pump
•    2 x 9.5L Jerry Cans

•    2mtr x 10mm Cold Pipe
•    2mtr x 20mm Waste Pipe
•    2mtr x 10mm Hot Pipe (Only available when mixer tap selected)
•    1 x 75mm Floor Vent

•    Pack of x 5 P Clips
•    4 x Jubilee Clips
•    1x 8mm Straight Compression Coupling

Camping Gaz:

•    1x Camping Gaz Regulator
•    1x 8mm Compression Nozzle
•    1mtr LPG Gas Hose

Bulkhead Option includes:

•    1 x 8mm Bulkhead Regulator
•    1 x 45cm Pigtail
•    1 x 8mm 90° Compression Elbow
•    1 x Gaz Adapter
•    2mtr x 8mm Copper Pipe

Product Name: Vango Faros III Air Low Campervan Awning
Product Description:
Vango Faros III Air Low Awning

Lightweight and easy to pitch drive away campervan awning

The Vango Faros III Air awning is a compact drive away awning designed for use with campervans. With a connection height of 180-21cm it is designed for use with VW T6 or similar sized vans and motorhomes. It is lightweight, quick and easy to set up, making it perfect for weekend camping and touring.

With a spacious living area which can be used as extra living space or camping storage, the Vango Faros Air provides a versatile multipurpose space outside your campervan. It's large front door can be rolled up or zipped closed. It has a secondary mesh door panel which can be used for added ventilation. The Faros also has a large side window and extra ventilation panels.

Perfect for short family stays, this touring awning attaches yo your campervan, extending your living space dramatically. As a drive away awning it can be quickly and easily detached from the van and left freestanding while you enjoy you holiday.

Packed with features

Vango have packed this awning with their typical fistful of features. This includes their TBS II Tension Band System, which brace the awning for better performance in wet and windy conditions, as well as reducing fabric sag. Pre-angled air beams provide better structure compared to traditional air beams. High-level AirZone ventilation panels work to reduce condensation, and the included privacy curtains can be toggled back or rolled away when not in use.

Upgrade for drive-away use

The Faros is ready to be used as a drive-away awning when used with the Vango Drive-Away Awning Kit, which is also available separately. This awning comes complete with a dual action pump (with pressure dial) for rapid inflation, as well as a carry bag. The awning is made from Sentinel's advanced active fabric, which is strong and fully waterproof. A fully sewn-in groundsheet is integrated into the awning, too, which groundsheet protectors available separately.

Vango Faros Air awning features:

  • Robust and waterproof Sentinel Active fabric
  • Pre-angled air beams with Vango AirSpeed valve system
  • Wind and rain tested to European standards
  • AirZone high level ventilation panels to reduce condensation.
  • Fully sewn-in groundsheet
  • High visibility guylines
  • Includes bag of steel pegs
  • Lantern hanging points included
  • Included roll away connecting tunnel
  • Twin doors for access
  • Front door can be raised on poles for extra cover (king poles sold separately)

Product Description:
Vision Plus Status 350 Omni-Directional Antenna with VP2 TV Amplifier 

360 degree TV aerial with powerful amplifier

The intelligent design behind this TV aerial allows it to receive TV broadcasting signals through 360 degrees, removing the need to direct and angle your aerial. What's more, it comes complete with the capable VP2 amplifier, boosting your signal to a strong and stable level.

High performance television signal reception

The Status 350 receives horizontal and vertical signals through a full 360 degrees, allowing it to pick up signals broadcast from any direction. The included VP2 amplifier incorporates variable gain adjustment, allowing your signal to be fine-tuned to match your conditions. 

A distinctive profile with performance benefits

Standard fitting options include both roof or mast mount, with an option sucker mount for easy temporary installation. The angle can also be adjusted by up to 15 degrees to suit uneven surfaces. The dome is designed to split at the neck in the event of an impact, keeping your motorhome, caravan or campervan roof safe and secure.

Status 350 antenna features:

  • Can receive both horizontal and vertical signals thru a full 360 degrees
  • Includes VP2 amplifier
  • Angle adjustable thru 15 degrees
  • Designed to keep roof secure in event of impact
  • Includes multiple fitting options
  • Easily removeable

Product Description:
Certikin iSAVER Swimming Pool Pump Drive Inverter

A low-cost way to reduce pool pump running costs

The Certikin iSAVER allows you to improve the energy efficiency of your existing pool pump equipment. It can control the rate of a fixed-speed swimming pool pump, which often run at a higher speed than is required for filtration efficiency. Lower pump speeds can also help to lengthen the lifespan of your pump, and will reduce pump noise output.

Enhanced control

The iSAVER comes equipped with a clear display for easy control, and also includes a timer feature allowing you to automate your pool pump. The energy savings from this device can be as high as 80%. Using efficiency-focused inverter technology, the iSAVER effectively turns your fixed-speed pool pump into a variable speed unit.

Certikin iSAVER features:

  • High contrast display panel with controls
  • Efficient inverter technology
  • Includes timer functionality for scheduled pump running times

Sandbanks Optimal Inflatable Kayak

Versatile all-rounder single seat designed to rival rigid kayaks

The Optimal is an excellent crossover kayak, providing speed on the flat and agility in white water conditions. Fully configurable

The Optimal is designed to feel like a rigid kayak, and includes features often omitted even on these. It includes a removeable seat, 4-piece paddle, lower leg support, a wheeled carry bag as well as a removeable skeg, which grants extra speed and stability at sea.

Product Description:
Reimo VW T5 T6 Campervan Rear Tailgate Tent Awning - Premium Trim

High quality campervan awning

The Reimo Premium rear tent for Transporter vans is the ultimate easy-pitch awning. By sliding over the boot of your vehicle, this awning requires no poles, keeping its weight to a minimum. This also means it has an extra short pitching time, taking the stress out of your holiday.

Luxury design

This rear tent awning comes with features designed to make your stay as comfortable as possible. This includes mosquito nets for all 3 doors, PVC windows in the roof for lighting, and enough space to fit a camp bed. The sides use tinted windows, and a skirting keeps you warm at night.

Lightweight and waterproof

Reimo have equipped this awning with 100% 190T Ripstop polyester, ensuring it is durable enough for your next journey. The fabric has a hydrostatic head of 3000mm, ensuring you have a dry night's sleep, and has a UV and fire resistant coating to ensure the fabric colour does not fade.

Reimo VW T5 T6 Tailgate Awning Features:

  • Skirting panel to prevent drafts
  • PVC window in roof
  • Tinted windows in sides
  • Three openable doorways
  • Lightweight pole-free design - uses boot opening for rigidity
  • Mosquito nets built into all three doors
  • Extra fast pitching time

Product Name: Outwell Universal Free Standing Inner Bedroom Tent
Product Description:
Outwell Free Standing Inner Tent

Versatile sleeping tent to erect inside awnings

This freestanding inner bedroom tent lets you add a mini bedroom to your awning, with room for up to two sleepers. Made of darkened polyester fabric, it permits very little light, ensuring you get a good night's sleep. The lightweight hollow core fibreglass poles provide the tent's rigidity, which means you don't need to attach to any interior awning fittings. This universal design also means the inner tent can be used in any awning in which it fits.

Product Name: Outwell Bremburg Air Campervan Drive Away Awning
Product Description:
Outwell Bremburg Air Campervan Drive Away Awning

Lightweight and easy to pitch campervan awning tent

Need more space in your campervan? This compact camper awning is perfect for friends, couples and families who need a little extra room. This drive-away awning can be left freestanding while you explore your destination in your campervan, saving you the hassle of packing it away - and letting you leave some of your supplies back on the campsite.

Be ready for any weather

The Bremburg Air comes complete with insect-proof mesh screens, ensuring your evenings aren't disturbed by any airborne insects. Outwell have also used their premium Outtex 4000 Select 100% polyester fabric for this awning, which has a hydrostatic head of 4000mm for excellent waterproofing.

Inflatable awning for easy setup

This awning uses Outwell's One Air System frame, which provides easy inflation via a single valved inflation point. 

Outwell Bremburg Air Campervan Awning Features:

  • Uses Outwell's Outtex 4000 100% polyester fabric
  • Roll-away doors for versatility
  • Twin side canopies
  • Can be attached to either side of van
  • Compatible with VW T5 T6
  • Double-coated waterproof polyethylene groundsheet
  • Heavy duty Outwell zips
  • Built-in draught excluder skirt
  • Pre-shaped air tubes provide excellent headroom
  • HookTrack system for up to 1.5kg of hanging lights etc

Product Name: Wolfrace VW T5/T6 Explorer Explore Matt Black Campervan Alloy Wheels
Product Description:
Wolfrace VW T5/T6 Explore Matt Black "Swamper" Campervan Alloy Wheels

Give your VW Transporter campervan the off-road swamper look with the Explore alloy wheel from wolfrace.

Overview

The Wolfrace Explore range is manufactured with a tough look and construction and with its mesh design provides your braking and suspension system with maximum protection allowing you to explore. Finished in matt black this alloy is popular with the swamper conversion however these alloys would finish any conversion off in style. 

Design

The explorer range is specially designed with campervans in mind providing the finishing touch to any campervan conversion. Available to purchase as a set of 4 alloys only or with all terrain BF Goodrich Tyres.

Vehicle Compatibility 

The Wolfrace Explorer Explore Matt Black is compatible with the below vans:

  • VW T5 Transporter & Caravelle 2003-2009
  • VW T5.1 Transporter & Caravelle 2010-15
  • VW T6 Transporter & Caravelle 2015-19
  • VW T6.1 Transporter & Caravelle 2019 Onwards

Product Name: Reimo Isoflex Thermomat for Renault Trafic & Vauxhall Vivaro Vans & Campers 2015-
Product Description:
Reimo Isoflex Thermomat for Renault Trafic & Vauxhall Vivaro Vans & Campers 2015-

Insulated cab windscreen and windows cover for vans and campervans

The Thermomat is an effective and low-cost way to keep your camper comfy all year round. The Thermomat uses 7 layers of Isoflex insulation, preventing excessive heat loss from your windows. On hot days, this insulation, combined with the reflective top layer, keeps your van from getting too hot, too.

Easy to fit

The Thermomat fixes to your windows with suction cups for easy and mark-free attachment and removal. It's designed to provide a bespoke fitting to Trafic and Vivaro vans, as well as other vans which share the same cab windows. This insulative cover also grants extra privacy, too.

Reimo Isoflex Thermomat features:

  • 3-part cab insulation for windscreen and cab side windows
  • Uses 7-layer Isoflex insulation
  • Reflects solar radiation
  • Also acts as a privacy screen
  • Compatible with:
    • Renault Trafic 2015-
    • Vauxhall Vivaro 2015-
    • Nissan NV300 2015-

Product Name: Renault Trafic Vauxhall Vivaro LWB Glass Campervan Window - UK Passenger Side Rear
Product Description:
Campervan Windows for Trafic/Vivaro - Bonded Privacy Glass Fixed Window - LWB

Passenger side fixed window for Renault Trafic, Vauxhall Vivaro, Nissan NV300 and Fiat Talento vans

Need some more light in your panel van conversion or work van? Manufactured to the OEM standard, this bonded van window is suitable for the Renault Trafic van platform, as well as its siblings the Vauxhall Vivaro, Nissan NV300 and Fiat Talento. These windows feature European 'E' marks, certifying that they meet European vehicular glass safety regulations.

Ideal for van conversions

Whether you are converting a Trafic or Vivaro Van into a campervan, or simply require more light in the Trafic van you work in, the Renault Trafic and Vauxhall Vivaro bonded windows are a neat, tidy and practical solution. The glass is also tempered, which means that in the case of an accident they will break into small pieces, instead of large, sharp shards.

Strength and privacy as standard

As with all our bonded windows, this bonded window for the Trafic or Vivaro models is tempered and features a permanent 80% tint which not only looks sleek, but also helps to reduce glare and UV in the van, as well as offering privacy to the user.

Compatible with the following vans:

  • Renault Trafic 2015- LWB
  • Vauxhall Vivaro 2015- LWB
  • Nissan NV300 2015- LWB
  • Fiat Talento 2015- LWB

Product Description:
Outwell Inner Tent for Milestone Bremburg Pine Hills & Daytona Awnings

Comfortable awning inner tent

Experience the ultimate in camping luxury with the Outwell Inner Tent. Designed to fit seamlessly within a range of Outwell awnings including Milestone, Daytona, Pine Hills, and Bremburg awnings, this inner tent offers a private and comfortable sleeping area for up to two people. This inner tent features darkened fabric, ensuring you have a comfortable light level in the evenings. The sides feature storage pockets to hold your belongings, and cable entry points allow convenient access for electronics.

Premium construction and materials 

Made with high-quality materials and featuring a spacious design, this inner tent provides the perfect solution for those who want to enjoy the great outdoors without sacrificing the comforts of home. With its easy set-up and durable construction, the Outwell Inner Tent is the ultimate choice for any campervan adventures.

Additional sleeping area

This inner tent, which is easy and quick to pitch, makes a bedroom for guests in next to no time. The sleeping area is amble for two and expands the sleeping capacity of your campervan significantly. This tent uses toggles to attach to your awning. The walls are made of breathable polyester, and the base uses a strong waterproof 75D fabric.

Product Description:
Campervan Bonded Privacy Glass with Window Ducato, Boxer, Relay L2/L3/L4 2006 onwards

Rear Barn Door window for Ducato, Relay and Boxer campervans

Manufactured to OEM standard, this bonded van window is suitable for the right hand variants of the Fiat Ducato, Relay and Boxer camper vans. Our tempered windows are 'E' stamped, which means they meet the strict European safety standard UN/ECE R43, ensuring this glass is safe for use on vehicles.

Ideal for van conversions

Whether you are converting a Fiat Ducato, Peugeot Boxer or Citroen Relay into a campervan, or simply require more light in the relay van you work in, these Fiat Ducato bonded windows are a neat, tidy and practical solution. These windows match the specifications of windows fitted in the factory by manufacturers, ensuring you are receiving a fully compatible and high quality window.

Strength and privacy as standard

As with all our bonded windows, this bonded window for the Ducato models is tempered and features a permanent 80% tint which not only looks sleek, but also helps to reduce glare and UV in the van, as well as offering privacy to the user. As these windows are tempered, they will shatter into small pieces instead of sharp shards when broken, reducing the chance of injury in the event of an accident substantially.

Campervan bonded window features:

  • Tempered glass ensures no sharp shards if broken
  • 80% privacy tinted
  • 'E' stamped to ensure compliance with strict European safety regulations on vehicle windows
  • Fritted glass - ceramic dot pattern at edges hides visibility of cut metal

Compatible with:

  • Fiat Ducato L2/L3/L4 2006 on
  • Citroen Relay L2/L3/L4 2006 on
  • Peugeot Boxer L2/L3/L4 2006 on

Product Name: Ultra Cure Campervan Window Adhesive Bundle with U-Trim
Product Description:
Ultra Cure Bonded Window Fitting Kit with Window Trim

High quality adhesive sealant for easy and safe window installation

This handy starter kit provides all you need to install one or more bonded windows to your campervan. Our kit uses high-quality Winbond bonding adhesive, which is specially designed for use with campervan windows. It's perfect for adding extra windows to your Transit, VW T5 or T6, Ducato or other panel vans.

Includes cleaner and primer

The kit includes primer, which allows the glue to create an excellent connection, as well as a specialist surface cleaner which maximises adhesion. Applicators and gloves are also included in this kit, helping you to get the most from the Winbond window adhesive compound. 

With rubber u-profile edging

We've included a rubber edging with this kit, which fits snugly over the cut-out created in your van to provide a flush seal, closing off the sharp metal edge. Select how many windows you're fitting above and we'll provide approximately the right amount of u-trim - while we provide enough to fit most windows with trim to spare, we can't guarantee it will be enough for every setup. 

Winbond Bonded Window Installation Kit Includes:

  • Winbond Ultra Cure bonding adhesive - 310ml
  • Winbond Ultra Cure primer - 30ml
  • Surface cleaner - 30ml
  • U-trim for 10-12mm panel edges
  • Pair of Gloves
  • Felt Applicator

Product Name: Single Core Auto Electrical Cable - 1mm - 16mm
Product Description:
Thin Wall Single Core Cable - 1mm²-16mm²

Suitable for high temperatures and low voltages

Our single core cable is manufactured to meet automotive standards, with high performance characteristics. It's sourced from a trusted supplier used throughout the automotive industry, making it perfect for reliable electrical installations in caravans, campervans, motorhomes, cars and boats. Available in Black & Red cable colours. 

Designed for 12v/24v use

This cable is designed for the voltages used in your campervan, motorhome, car or boat. This means it's safe to run at 12v or 24v, with a maximum voltage of 60v. The thin wall gives this cable a reduced weight, providing considerable weight and volume savings when used in wiring harnesses. The PVC insulation is also resistant to petrol, diesel and lubricating oils, as well as abrasions and cuts.

Ultra durable

On top of the physical resistance offered by this high-grade insulation, this cable is also rated for temperature ranges of between -40ºC to 105ºC, with a short term peak limit of 120ºC. The copper conductor core meets industry standards and safety regulations too, including ISO 6722-1:2011 (Class B) and BS EN 60228:2005.

Thin wall single core cable features:

  • Designed for 12/24v use, with max voltage of 60v
  • Can handle temperatures of up to -40ºC to 105ºC, with a short term limit of 120ºC
  • Thin wall gives considerable weight and space savings
  • Insulation is resistant to cuts, abrasions, petrol, diesel and lubricating oils

*All Cable is sold as a complete roll or in 10 metre increments

Product Description:
Thin Wall Twin Core Auto Electrical Cable - 1mm²-4.5mm²

Durable cables designed for 12v/24v use

Our cables are sourced from a trusted automotive supplier, providing reliable performance across the industry. These cables use a thin, flat insulation layer to provide excellent weight savings and space savings. Available outer-sheath colour black, inner-core colours include black & red.

Extra durable

These cables use a tough PVC insulation, which provides resistance to cuts and abrasions, as well as petrol, diesel and lubricating oils. It's also resistant to extreme temperatures, withstanding conditions between -40ºC to 105ºC - with short term peak temperatures of up to 120ºC.

Ideal for campervan use

This cable is designed for use in 12v-24v use, with a maximum recommended voltage of 60v. This makes it perfect for use in campervans, caravans, motorhomes and boats.

Twin core cable features:

  • Suitable for 12-24v use, with max voltage of 60v
  • Thin wall offers substantially reduced weight and volume for your wiring system
  • Resistant to petrol, diesel and oils
  • Can withstand temperature ranges -40ºC to 105ºC with short term peak temps of 120ºC
  • Slash-resistant PVC insulation

*All Cable is sold as a complete roll or in 10 metres increments

Flexi Battery Cable Wire - 25mm - 50mm
Product Description:
Flexi Battery Cable Wire - 25mm² - 50mm²

Premium Automotive Battery Cables

Introducing our robust range of Automotive Battery Cables, available in models 934, 936, PVC70, and PVC95. Designed to deliver exceptional performance, these cables are your reliable partner for automotive, marine, and allied industry applications. With optional colors of Red or Black, customize your cabling solution to fit your needs perfectly.

Key Features:

Classic PVC Low Voltage Cables

Our cables are crafted with the highest standards of quality to ensure durability and reliability across various applications.

  • Standard Compliance: Manufactured to BS6862 Part 1 1971 standards.
  • Material: Plain copper conductors with PVC insulation.
  • Temperature Range (934 & 936): Operates efficiently between -15°C to 70°C.
  • Temperature Range (PVC70 & PVG95): Operates efficiently between -30°C to 70°C.
  • Voltage Compatibility: Suitable for 12v and 24v systems (up to a maximum of 100v).
  • Chemical Resistance: Resistant to petrol, diesel, lubricating oils, and diluted acids.

PVC Battery Cables 934 & 936

PVC Battery Cables PVC70 & PVC95

Designed for High Load Applications:

Our automotive battery cables are engineered to handle high battery or starter loads, making them ideal for car starting systems, campervan charging systems, and more.

  • High Conductivity: Large conductive cross-section ensures low resistance and high current rating.
  • Temperature Resilience: PVC insulative sheath rated for temperatures from -15°C to 70°C.
  • Durability: Sourced from a trusted supplier, our cables guarantee safety and compliance, trusted throughout the automotive industry.

Ideal Applications:

Perfect for use in car starting systems, campervan electrical setups, and other high-load battery applications. Whether you are outfitting a vehicle or a marine vessel, our battery cables deliver the performance you need for reliable power management.

Choose Reliability:

Equip your electrical systems with our premium range of Automotive Battery Cables. With a variety of specifications and customizable options, we have the right solution for your power needs. Trust in cables that are designed to last, perform, and exceed your expectations.

CF Parker Baby Cooker, Oven and Hob for Camping 

The CF Parker Baby Cooker is the perfect small, portable gas cooker for camping and awnings.

The CF Parker Baby Cooker is a small, portable gas cooker that is designed for use in tight spaces, ideal for outdoor use when camping and in awnings attached to campervans, caravans and motorhomes.

Product Name: Vitrifrigo D20A 12v Drawer Fridge Freezer for Campervans
Product Description:
Vitrifrigo D20A Compact 12v Drawer Fridge for Campervans

Mini drawer fridge, perfect for small campervans

This sleek drawer fridge lets you fit your refrigeration into compact spaces, such as under bed or within a cupboard system. With 20 litres of space, you can store all your food and drinks for a short trip. It also runs off R600a natural refrigerant, an eco-friendly refrigerant gas which maintains performance.

Versatile and powerful compressor

The D20A gives you greater installation freedom by allowing you to install the compressor system (the kit that provides the fridge's cooling power) up to 1.5 metres away from the fridge. This also means the fridge itself doesn't have to accommodate the compressor, providing extra space for storage volume and insulation. Alternatively the cooler can be mounted on the back of the fridge.

Fridge or freezer

Use the LED control panel to switch between fridge or freezer operation modes. There are four temperature levels for fridge operation, as well as a freezer mode which can cool as low as -10°C. The sleep mode ensures quiet compressor operation overnight, too.

In fridge mode you can choose 4 levels of temperature, to change set push the button F.

From left to right:

  • Set 1: 0-2°C
  • Set 2: 2-4°C
  • Set 3: 4-6°C
  • Set 4: 6-8°C

Vitrifrigo D20A fridge features:

  • Operates on 12v or 24v, ideal for campervans, caravans, motorhomes and boats
  • Includes low voltage cut-out and high voltage protection
  • Compressor can be removed and moved up to 1.5m away for versatile installation
  • LED control panel
  • Four fridge temperature levels selectable
  • Can be used as a freezer, cooling as low as -10°C
  • Night mode included for quiet operation while sleeping
  • Two side catches keep door secure in transit - opened via chrome finished handle

Please note: Due to the design of a fridge with a removable compressor, extra care must be taken when moving the fridge and demount-able compressor unit itself
Product Warranty: 24 Month Warranty on all Vitrifrigo fridges

Product Description:
Vitrifrigo D30A 12v Compressor Drawer Fridge

Compact 30 litre drawer fridge freezer

Fit a fridge in any vehicle with a compact Vitrifrigo drawer fridge freezer. This D30A measures just 250mm high by 440mm wide, yet an innovative design gives it 30 litres of space, including enough width to fit a typical plastic bottle. It also runs off R600a natural refrigerant, an eco-friendly refrigerant gas which maintains performance.

With relocatable cooling compressor

The D30A features a compressor which can be moved up to 1.5m away from the fridge itself, allowing for flexible installations to suit any van or camper. This also allows the fridge to maximise on volume and insulation. For more conventional installations, the cooling compressor can be fitted to the rear of the fridge, too.

LED controls with sleep mode and freezer mode

The integrated LED controls let you activate sleep mode, which reduces the fridge's noise to a whisper, lets you cycle between four fridge cooling levels, and also lets you switch to freezing mode.

Vitrifrigo D30A fridge features:

  • Central chrome handle latches door shut for safe transit
  • Night mode provides quiet and economical operation while asleep

Product Description:
Vitrifrigo Slim 90 Compressor Fridge Freezer 12v

Super compact 90 litre fridge, ideal for campervans

The Vitrifrigo Slim 90 is designed to offer the maximum refrigeration volume in restricted spaces. Into its slim dimensions it fits 82 litres of total storage volume, with a 10-litre 3-star freezer compartment, which can cool as low as -18°C. The fridge uses the new, natural and eco-friendly refrigerant R600a for excellent performance.

With versatile compressor mounting

The Slim 90 offers extra installation possibilities thanks to its cooling unit, which can be installed as far as 1.5m away from the fridge itself. This allows the fridge to maximise on internal volume, and lets your installation match the contours of your vehicle. The door is also reversible, ensuring it is ideal for use in any vehicle.

Fully featured and with LED controls

The integrated LED control panel lets you switch between various modes for the refrigerator, including an ultra quiet sleep mode and a rapid cooling turbo mode. The fridge is available in two finishes - a glossy white fridge with a pearly effect, and a matt black fridge with an anti-fingerprint, scratch-resistant and soft-touch finish.

Vitrifrigo Slim 90 fridge features:

  • Total capacity of 82 litres, with 10 litre freezer compartment
  • Three star freezer can freeze to temperatures as low as -18°C
  • Uses eco-friendly and efficient R600a natural gas refrigerant
  • Relocatable compressor cooling unit can be moved up to 1.5m away
  • Runs on 12/24v - ideal for campervan, caravan, motorhome or boat use
  • Integrated LED control panel
  • Turbo mode for rapid cooling
  • Sleep mode for quiet operation
  • Available in matte black or glossy, pearl effect white
  • Dimensions see image

Product Description:
Vitrifrigo TL43 Top Loading Chest 12v Compressor Fridge 

Versatile compressor powered box freezer

Maximise your storage space with a top-loading fridge. This cooler can be loaded up to the brim thanks to the top-loading design, and includes two removeable food containers which sit flush on the top to utilise all of the available space.

Run for 3+ days on a single 100ah battery

The compressor unit is relocatable, allowing you to install it up to 1.5m away to suit the space available in your campervan, motorhome or caravan.

This fridge includes a control panel, allowing you to activate night mode for quiet operation while sleeping, and a turbo mode for rapid cooling - perfect for chilling drinks in a hurry. Integrated LED lighting make it easy to find what you need, too.

Robust 12v stainless steel compressor fridge

Need a fridge that's built to last? This extra tough 150 litre stainless steel fridge from Vitrifrigo is designed to withstand the rigours of travel. It uses a marine-grade stainless steel, which is resistant to rust and highly durable.

Dual drawer system

Thanks to the powerful and efficient 12v compressor, you can customize your refrigerator's layout. Both drawers an act as fridge, or both as freezer - or you can set one as freezer, and one as fridge, giving you total control. This can be set on the digital control panel along the front of the fridge, which lets you set a target temperature as low as -18°C - which it can reach even in air temperatures as high as 43°C.

Frost-free design with versatile compressor mounting

The fridge's compressor can be mounted up to 1.5m away if required, allowing it to fit wherever is convenient for your campervan, caravan, motorhome or boat. It uses Vitrifrigo's marine secure Steelock door latch, and uses interior LED lighting for excellent visibility.

  • Marine grade stainless steel
  • 150 litres of volume
  • Digital control panel for easy temperature control
  • Each drawer can act as fridge or freezer independently, or both can act as the same
  • Door includes a ventilation latch position to prevent odour build-up whne the unit is switched off
  • Fridge frame can be mounted flush or proud
  • Frost-free design
  • With interior LED lighting

Product Name: Victron Cerbo GX MK2 Electrical Control Hub
Product Description:
Victron Cerbo GX MK2 Electrical Communication Hub

Maximise the performance from your electrical system 

Control your Victron electrical system from one place with the Cerbo GX hub. This bespoke control unit allows your discrete Victron electrical units to communicate with each other.

Advanced data and control

The Cerbo GX MK2 provides important metrics such as battery SoC (state of charge), power consumption, power harvest from solar, generator or mains, tank levels and temperature measurements. You can use this information to make decisions on your shore power input current limit, automatically start or stop generators, and change other parameters to optimise your system.

With many I/O options

The Cerbo contains a plethora of inputs, including multiple USB ports, general purpose digital inputs, Victron VE.Direct connectors, CAN bus, 2 relays, temperature ports and tank level ports. With this connectivity you can control up to 25 VE.Can solar chargers, for example. 

Powerful processor

The Cerbo uses an efficient dual-core processor to process your system's performance data, allowing a wide number of inputs and fast analysis. You can use the VictronConnect app to communicate with the Cerbo via Bluetooth, or connect via the Victron Remote Management system for easy configuration of your system's rules and scheduling.

With optional touchscreen

The Cerbo GX Touch 5" touchscreen features a waterproof display and easy installation. It's perfect for configuring your system for optimised energy usage.

Victron Cerbo GX features:

  • Dual core processor
  • Huge number of available inputs
  • Expanded connectivity with dual VE.Can ports
  • With Bluetooth for smartphone monitoring and control
  • Includes two relays for switching devices
  • Automatic scheduling features included to turn off devices on a timer
  • Can be mounted via standard DIN-rail with small DIN-35 adapter
  • Waterproof design to resist damage
  • Compatible with VRM (Victron Remote Monitoring) online system

Victron Cerbo example uses:

  • Off-grid generators: Auto start/stop your generator, with ability to delay ignition until end of 'quiet' period
  • Energy storage systems: Keep backup batteries at 100%, kick in power during power cuts, divert excess solar power to self-consumption to save money

Product Name: Victron Energy MultiPlus II 12/3000 12V Inverter Mains Charger VE.Bus
Product Description:
Victron Energy MultiPlus-II 12/3000/120-32 230V Inverter Mains Charger VE.Bus

The Victron MultiPlus-II combines the advanced functionality of the MultiPlus, and the grid-optimization features of the MultiGrid to create a fantastic all-in-one powerhouse perfect for powering your off-grid and grid-connected systems, making it perfect for caravanning, yachting & camping. Different from the MultiPlus, the MultiPlus-II has additional functionalities including an external current sensor which extends PowerControl and PowerAssist functions and optimises power consumption. The MultiPlus-II delivers unmatched performance in a compact and user-friendly design, making it ideal for campervans, caravans and motorhomes, and solar & off-grid setups.

The MultiPlus-II integrates an AC transfer switch which is built-in, allowing Uninterruptable Power Supply (UPS) on the main AC output. This means that in the event of power failure such as grid outage, shore power disconnect, or generator failure, the MultiPlus-II automatically switches on and takes over AC supply within milliseconds to ensure your connected devices continue operating without interruption. This lightning-fast transition (less than 20 milliseconds) allows your equipment to continue to operate without any disruption. Optional remote capabilities can be integrated into the MultiPlus-II device. By pairing your MultiPlus-II with a GX device (such as the Cerbo GX), you gain access to a comprehensive suite of features via the free VRM app and VRM portal website. Monitor your system's performance, control settings, and even automate functions like starting a backup generator – all from your smartphone, tablet, laptop, or PC. This remote access ensures you stay informed and in control, no matter your location. (Note: GX device sold separately).

Key Features:

  • PowerControl & PowerAssist: The MultiPlus II prevents overloading of limited AC sources (generators, shore power) by strategically managing battery power and AC input. It boosts available power when needed, ensuring optimal performance.
  • True Sine Wave Inverter: Provides clean and reliable AC power, capable of running most appliances seamlessly. Delivers exceptional peak power surge capacity for handling demanding loads.
  • Advanced Battery Charger: The intelligent multi-stage charger ensures optimal charging for various battery types (wet, AGM, GEL, Li-ion), extending battery life.
  • Uninterrupted AC Power (UPS): In the event of a grid failure or power interruption, the MultiPlus-II seamlessly takes over within milliseconds, keeping your devices powered without disruption.
  • Ideal for Energy Storage Systems (ESS): The MultiPlus II is perfect for use in combination with MPPT solar chargers and other Victron energy devices. In the event of a grid failure, or when shore or generator power is disconnected, the MultiPlus can act as a UPS, providing uninterrupted AC power. It does this by activating its inverter to take over supply to your connected loads. It's able to do this in less than 20 milliseconds, which is so fast that even complex electronic devices such as computers will operate without disruption.
  • Expandable Power: Up to 6 units can operate in parallel for significantly increased power output. Ideal for high-demand applications.
  • Remote Monitoring & Control (Optional): When paired with a GX device (e.g., Cerbo GX), you can monitor and control your MultiPlus-II remotely via the free VRM app and VRM portal website. Accessible from anywhere in the world using your smartphone, tablet, laptop, or PC.
  • External Current Transformer Option: The MultiPlus-II enables enhanced PowerControl and PowerAssist functionality, allowing for precise current sensing (up to 32A) for optimized self-consumption.
  • Built-in Anti-Islanding: Provides crucial safety for off-grid applications by preventing the inverter from feeding electricity back to the utility grid in case of a disconnect.

Product Name: Victron Energy Lynx Power In DC Busbar for Battery Systems
Product Description:
Victron Energy Lynx Power In DC Busbar for Battery Systems

Victron Energy Lynx Power In DC Busbar

Connecting batteries efficiently in your DC power system is now easier with the Victron Energy Lynx Power In DC Busbar. This guide explores its features, functionalities, and benefits.

What it is:

  • A modular DC busbar system for battery connection in the Lynx DC distribution system.
  • Offers positive and negative busbars with four connection points for batteries, loads, chargers, and earth.
  • Requires external fusing for connected components (no built-in fuses).

Key Features:

  • High Current Rating: Suitable for various applications with its 1000A rating.
  • Modular Design: Expandable by connecting multiple units for more connections.
  • Improved Organisation: The Victron Energy Lynx Power In DC Busbar Simplifies wiring and maintenance with a clean layout.
  • Weather Resistance: IP22 rated for dust and water protection, ideal for outdoor use.
  • Compatibility: Seamless integration with Lynx Distributor and Shunt VE for monitoring and control.

How it Works:

  1. Connecting Batteries: Each unit offers four positive and negative connection points for parallel connection to increase capacity.
  2. Distribution to Loads: Connect your DC loads (inverters, refrigerators, etc.) to the terminals for efficient power distribution.
  3. Integration with Other Lynx Modules: Combine with Distributor for fused distribution and Shunt VE for system-wide battery monitoring.

Benefits:

  • Saves Space: Compact and space-saving compared to traditional wiring methods.
  • Simplified Wiring: Reduces complexity and makes installation easier.
  • Enhanced Safety: Organised connections promote safety and easier troubleshooting.
  • Scalability: The Victron Energy Lynx Power In DC Busbar adapts to growing power needs by adding additional units.

Overall, the Victron Energy Lynx Power In DC Busbar offers a reliable and efficient solution for battery connection and management in your DC power system. Its modular design, high current rating, and compatibility with other Lynx modules make it a versatile choice for multiple applications.

High durability and efficiency for year-round power

Perfect for low-cost off-grid use as well as campervan caravan motorhome and marine use. This capable Victron 60w solar panel helps to power your devices and recharge your batteries even when disconnected from mains hook-up. Victron's 60w solar panel features an exceptionally low voltage-temperature coefficient, which in layman's terms means that it has excellent performance even in high temperatures.

Guaranteed efficiency

This Victron solar panel provides excellent performance, capturing energy from light across the entire solar spectrum. A high sensitivity to light ensures it operates well in low light conditions, too. You can be confident that this performance will continue for years to come thanks to Victron's 25-year warranty on the solar panels performance, and 5-year warranty on the materials and workmanship.

Rugged design

This Victron solar panel uses an anodized aluminium design, which can be roof-mounted to most common mounting systems. A sealed, waterproof junction box keeps your cabling dry and secure. Tempered glass increases impact resistance, too, and is designed for high light transmission.  The 60W solar panel from Victron is ideal for caravan motorhome campervan and marine applications.

Victron Energy BlueSolar solar panel features:

  • Low voltage-temperature coefficient for excellent hot temperature performance
  • Exceptional low-light performance
  • Sensitive to light across the solar spectrum
  • Sealed, waterproof junction box
  • High performance bypass diodes minimise power drop in shade
  • Advanced EVA (Ethylene Vinyl Acetate) coating for enhanced safety and performance

Product Name: Victron Energy Peak Power Pack - 12.8V, 40AH, 512WH LiFePO4 Battery with Mains Charger and Solar/Alternator Charging
Product Description:
Victron Energy Peak Power Pack - 12.8V, 40AH, 512WH

Provide high currents for short times, without the limitations of lead acid batteries

Victron's peak power pack provides a complete alternative for traditional lead acid batteries. It's designed for applications such as caravan movers, where batteries need to provide a lot of power for a short time - and then face little demand for the rest of the time. 

With low discharge LiFePO4 batteries, built-in charger and solar

The peak power pack includes two discrete inputs, one for solar or alternator charging, and another for mans charging, each with current and voltage control built-in. There's also two outputs - one high-load output designed for caravan movers, and another output for low-voltage 'domestic' use, each with short-circuit and excess discharge protection. This means you can use this battery system as your primary leisure battery, too.

Easy to use and monitor

The battery includes a dual-colour LED and push button which indicates charge level, and also indicates any error codes for easy diagnosis of issues in your system. You can also engage a Storage mode for the Peak Power Pack, which reduces self-discharge, allowing it to be kept in storage for a year. It's also compatible with Victron's VE.Direct system for easy mobile monitoring on your smartphone.

Victron Energy Peak Power Pack features:

  • Lightweight and high performance
  • With 'domestic' output to act as leisure battery for caravan or motorhome
  • High load output for caravan movers
  • With both mains charger and alternator/solar charger
  • Storage mode for ultra low self discharge
  • Dual-colour LED and push button for checking state of charge and error diagnosis
  • Compatible with VE.Direct

Victron Energy Lynx Distributor
Product Description:
Victron Energy Lynx Distributor

Modular DC busbar system with four fuses

The Victron Lynx Distributor is composed of two busbars, one positive and negative. The positive busbar has four fuse-protected connections, with each fuse monitored by the system. If a fuse is broken, the respective LED on the front of the unit reflects this. If connected to other Lynx monitoring devices, such as the Lynx Smart BMS, it will report the broken fuse to this unit also, which can in turn report it to your smartphone via VictronConnect. The MEGA fuses for the unit need to be purchased separately to ensure you use the correct fuse rating for your campervan, caravan or off-grid electrical system.

Product Name: Victron Energy BlueSolar PWM Charge Controller w/LCD Display & USB
Product Description:
Victron Energy BlueSolar PWM Solar Charge Controller w/LCD Display & USB 5amp, 10 amp and 20amp

Powerful and easy to monitor battery charger 

With a new ultra-low-power LCD display, it's easier than ever to monitor your battery's charge levels and system status. The BlueSolar PWM gives you controllable battery charging from your solar panels, with multiple protections to prevent common issues.

Three stage charging

The BlueSolar uses three-stage battery charging, with a bulk, absorption and float mode to maximise the efficiency of each type of charging. Each stage can be programmed to optimise your setup. It also contains a lighting control function, providing extra control to your campervan, caravan, motorhome, boat or off-grid setup. The BlueSolar contains pre-programmed algorithms for optimal charging of AGM, GEL, flooded and LiFePo4 batteries.

With protections to prevent failure

The BlueSolar PWM includes a programmable load output with low voltage and a manual disconnect. This output is protected against both over load and short circuit, and the BlueSolar protects against reverse polarity connection of both the solar panels or battery. It also features two 5V USB outputs for easy access, too.

Victron Energy BlueSolar PWM Charge Controller Features:

  • Low power LCD display for easy monitoring and programming
  • Lighting control function - programmable with buttons on interface
  • Three-stage battery charging - bulk, absorption & float
  • Two 5V USB outputs
  • Programmable load output with low voltage & manual disconnect
  • Load output protected against over load & short circuit
  • BlueSolar protects against reverse polarity of solar panels and/or battery
  • Option to schedule load output on/off times

Product Description:
Victron Orion-Tr Smart Non-Isolated DC to DC Battery Charger (ORI241236140)

Adaptive 3-stage charger with smartphone control

The Victron Orion-Tr Smart is ideal for use in dual-battery scenarios, where an alternator and starter battery charge a leisure battery. It utilised a fully programmable battery charge algorithm, and is compatible with smart alternators. It can detect when the engine is running also to adapt the charging procedure.

Full control

The Victron Orion-Tr Smart regulates the charging process with an efficient 3-stage charging algorithm. This includes a bulk, absorption and float procedure, with programmable control to suit different battery technologies. The Victron Orion-Tr Smart supports Bluetooth, which enables wireless monitoring, control and software updates. A relay can also operated via a two-pole connector on the unit, enabling on-off control.

With short-circuit and high temperature protection

The Orion-Tr is protected from short circuits, reducing the chance of damage from faulty wiring. They can also be connected in parallel to increase the output of your current. The Victron Orion-Tr Smart features IP43 protection when installed with the screw terminals downwards and uses an input fuse to offer additional protection.

Victron Energy Orion-Tr Smart 24/12-30 features:

  • 3-stage charging algorithm with bulk, absorption and float
  • Programmable Battery charging modes
  • Smart alternator support with engine running detection mechanism
  • On-off relay contact with two-pole connector
  • Short-circuit protection
  • High temperature protection
  • IP43 rated
  • Part No: ORI241236140
